  "description": "It\u0026rsquo;s been a bit since I\u0026rsquo;ve written much about it directly, since things keep moving around faster than it felt useful to write about them, but this evening, it feels appropriate to write a bit to plan out what is becoming known as \u0026ldquo;the Emsemioverse,\u0026rdquo; which is the shape my digital data and how i work with it is taking.\nThis log is written for myself and other agents working in that universe to help us understand what my goals are and how I picture getting there.\n",
